Macros
------

1.  qa = Record macro mapped to "a"

2.  qb = Record macro mapped to "b"

3.  @a = Repeat macro "a"

4.  @@ = Repeat last macro


Use macros with file "tmp_tps"

1.  :o tmp_tps

2.  VG (select everything)

3.  ~ (downcase)

4.  qb

5.  w (cursor on "s")

6.  i: ESC

7.  j^

8.  q (end recording)

9.  @b (play back on current line)

10. @@ (repeat once)

11. 5@@ (repeat 5 times)

12. CTRL-v (enter visual block mode)

13. G (select to last line)

14. I (insert before)

15. t. ESC 
